 !important; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><p style="padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(71, 69, 69); font-size: 18px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">一、教习礼仪：佛门日常行仪，寺院规约。</span></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"></section><p style="padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(71, 69, 69); font-size: 18px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">二 、寺院巡礼：参拜佛殿，感受水神山佛国净土的清净与庄严。</span></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"></section><p style="padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(71, 69, 69); font-size: 18px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">三、法师开示：恭敬聆听大德高僧的慈悲精彩讲座，为人生的道路点亮明灯，解除生活烦恼的束缚，将善心善行真正的体现在生活的点滴，佛法与生活紧密结合，跟随佛陀的脚步，走向解脱大道。</span></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"></section><p style="padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(71, 69, 69); font-size: 18px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">四、行禅坐禅：静定结合，内外兼修，既在红尘浪中，又在孤峰之上，在语默动静中保持心灵的自在与安详。</span></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"></section><p style="padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(71, 69, 69); font-size: 18px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">五、诵经礼佛：在天籁般的梵呗声中，口诵身拜，降服我慢，在流传千年的经文中，领略经典的慈悲与智慧。</span></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"></section><p style="padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(71, 69, 69); font-size: 18px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">六、报国问道：法师们的棒喝点拨，倾诉感想与困惑，聆听指导与开示，解开内心的烦恼，观受想行识，生禅定智慧。</span></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"></section><p style="padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(71, 69, 69); font-size: 18px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"